headline: SL Green Teams Up With Rockpoint for 100 Park Avenue, Sells 49% Stake
summary: SLG's JV with Rockpoint to sell a 49% stake in 100 Park Avenue values the Midtown office tower at $425 million, boosting balance sheet flexibility.
